81
00:05:33,230 --> 00:05:34,370
Saya tidak faham lagi.

82
00:05:35,140 --> 00:05:36,620
Tak kisahlah.

83
00:05:38,150 --> 00:05:39,206
Aksesori itu kelihatan hebat!

84
00:05:39,230 --> 00:05:40,230
Datang.

85
00:05:46,390 --> 00:05:47,390
Apa pendapat anda?

86
00:05:47,590 --> 00:05:48,590
Saya akan cuba yang lain.

87
00:05:53,710 --> 00:05:54,710
