Liao Tingyan!

93
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:07,800
Bukankah Liao Tingyan sudah mati?

94
00:06:08,470 --> 00:06:09,470
Mari kita lihat lebih dekat.

95
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:13,210
Di antara dua ini,

96
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:14,740
