129
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:19,440
Tuan...

130
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:21,440
Berhenti!

131
00:08:24,590 --> 00:08:25,326
Tuan...

132
00:08:25,350 --> 00:08:26,350
pergi pergi...

133
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,370
Lelaki yang pelik!

134
00:08:29,710 --> 00:08:31,570
Tuan Muda, mungkin kami telah melakukan kesilapan.

135
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,720
Adakah itu benar-benar bukan Liao Tingyan?

136
