151
00:09:45,230 --> 00:09:46,570
Saya keluar sendiri.

152
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,450
Ruling bersama saya.

153
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,640
Anda semakin berani dan lebih berani.

154
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,330
Sekarang awak pun berani menipu saya.

155
00:10:03,710 --> 00:10:05,300
Saya takut awak akan curiga

156
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:06,850
Memerintah jika saya memberitahu anda kebenaran.

157
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:09,056
Lagipun, dia adalah
Puan Istana Yin.

158
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,536
Dia mungkin bersubahat dengan keluarga Shi.

159
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:11,810
