169
00:10:28,470 --> 00:10:31,030
Jadi intinya awak tak
nak saya buang darah awak, kan?

170
00:10:39,510 --> 00:10:40,510
Sima Jiao yang busuk,

171
00:10:41,630 --> 00:10:43,020
